 07:45:32','2011-07-06 07:45:32',1),(29,'应该能确定是公司的防火墙把这个地址给拉黑了。换了源以后果真还不好使。。。\r\n我想安装解压zip的工具包，除了apt-get以外，怎么安装还方便点？',8,'2011-07-07 00:56:08','2011-07-07 00:56:08',8),(30,'If you could not use __apt-get__ to install package automatically, so the easier way is to download a Debian package of the software that you needed. Then run the following command in the terminal to install the package:\r\n\r\n    dpkg -i packagename.deb\r\n\r\nIf there is no Debian package of the software, the last resort you can only use is to download a source code tarball, then uncompress the package, configure, compile and install it manually.\r\n\r\n    tar -jxf packagename.tar.bz2 (tar -zxf packagename.tar.gz)\r\n    ./configure\r\n    make\r\n    make install',8,'2011-07-07 12:57:47','2011-07-07 13:45:42',3),(31,'到这个网址下载安装就好了：\r\nhttp://packages.ubuntu.com/maverick/i386/unzip/download\r\n\r\n注意： \r\n\r\n - `maverick` 是10.10的codename,你可以用`lsb_release -c` 这个命令查看你自己的系统版本，不一样的话要替换\r\n - 再看一下你的操作系统是不是64位的（注意是软件系统不是硬件平台，64位的机器上也能装32位系统），用`uname -a` 如果看见输出中有`64`字样的话，就把`i386`替换成`amd64`\r\n\r\n',8,'2011-07-07 13:22:24','2011-07-07 13:26:02',1),(32,'明白，哈哈',9,'2011-07-08 01:23:44','2011-07-08 01:23:44',11),(33,'Thank you very much! I see.',8,'2011-07-08 03:54:02','2011-07-08 03:54:02',8),(34,'我周一去给42期上课，t-shirt 估计周一周二的就能好\r\n',11,'2011-07-08 08:47:18','2011-07-08 08:47:18',1),(35,'有衣服穿了',11,'2011-07-08 12:40:01','2011-07-08 12:40:01',7),(36,'very humorous ! want to follow you  ,learn with you ,talk with you ,Worship you for the teacher.And I will try my best to  do it  !\r\n',7,'2011-07-08 13:44:44','2011-07-08 13:44:44',17),(37,'>it\'s me zhaodsh\r\n\r\nwelcome!\r\n\r\n>the site is very cool. so I decide to make one , but have other styles.....\r\n\r\nwill you do it in PHP? I highly recommend Ruby on Rails.\r\n\r\n>may I write some blogs on this ?\r\n\r\nit will be really nice if you can write some blog entry and share your coding experience with guys here. Thanks :)\r\n',12,'2011-07-08 14:30:20','